      "span_text": "In the first project  , a total of 210 healthy subjects (men and women aged 40-65 years, non-smokers) were randomised to one of six groups (n 35) supplemented for 8 months with either (g/d): placebo oil 10, olive oil 10, evening primrose (Oenothera biennis) oil 5 þ placebo oil 5, soyabean oil 5 þ placebo oil 5; tuna oil 5 (0·30 g EPA, 1·35 g DHA) þ placebo oil 5, evening primrose oil 5 þ tuna oil 5.",
